-- Level 3 Calls for Conditions to Comcast’s NBC Acquisition
-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 2010-12-17T02:41:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-17/level-3-calls-for-conditions-to-be-imposed-on-comcast-s-nbc-acquisition.html
Level 3 Communications Inc. Chief
Executive Officer James Q. Crowe asked U.S. officials to impose
conditions on Comcast Corp. and the company’s proposed
acquisition of NBC Universal, according to an e-mailed statement
from Level 3.  Crowe’s requested conditions include prohibiting Comcast
from using its control over access to subscribers to charge
Internet “backbone” carriers for interconnection to its
network.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  